  <task><p>Fill in the rest of the table for ten days. Round off decimal results to the nearest whole number.</p></task>
  
  <task><p>Use the third column of the table to plot the total number of infected residents, <m>I</m>, against time, <m>t</m>. Connect your data points with a smooth curve.</p>
